      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Marcel Vanthoor</b>\n</p><p><b>Marcel Vanthoor</b>,<br />\na Dutch software engineer and computer chess programmer. He has already written a very basic chess program in <a href=\"/Pascal#TurboPascal\" title=\"Pascal\">Turbo Pascal</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, \nand started a chess programming comeback in 2020 with his didactic chess engine <a href=\"/Rustic\" title=\"Rustic\">Rustic</a> written in <a href=\"/Rust\" title=\"Rust\">Rust</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n<i>Progress on Rustic</i> is topic of his <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a> thread, explaining all his development trials <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2019\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2019</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2020\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2021\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2021</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_Vanthoor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2019\">2019</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_Vanthoor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2019\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=71288\">Stockfish 10 x64 Level ELO's (WIP)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 15, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71384\">Stockfish vs. Lc0: IMHO disappointing result for Lc0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 27, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero#Lc0\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Lc0</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020\">2020</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_Vanthoor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2020\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73164\">New chess engine: Rustic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 23, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Rustic\" title=\"Rustic\">Rustic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73198\">Don't understand CarryRippler</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Traversing_Subsets_of_a_Set#AllSubsetsofanySet\" title=\"Traversing Subsets of a Set\">Carry-Rippler</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73493\">Where to enter/read position into hash table in perft?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 28, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73577\">Perft speed optimization</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 06, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75129\">Progress on Rustic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 16, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75342\">Determining evaluation by a genetic algorithm</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 09, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming#GeneticAlgorithm\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">Genetic Algorithms</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75549\">Principal Variation Search vs. Transposition Table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 26, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation\" title=\"Principal Variation\">Principal Variation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75573\">Make engine stop repeating moves in a clearly won position</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 27, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75944\">CECP \"time\" and \"otim\"</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 30, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">CECP</a>, <a href=\"/Time_Management\" title=\"Time Management\">Time Management</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2021\">2021</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_Vanthoor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2021\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76750\">SEE (Static Exchange Evaluation) pruning nodes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 01, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76787\">Your motivation for writing a chess engine?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 05, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77427\">Hitting a wall at ~1860 Elo</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 02, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_Vanthoor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/mvanthoor\">mvanthoor (Marcel Vanthoor) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://rustic-chess.org/\">About - Rustic Chess Engine</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_Vanthoor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=71288\">Stockfish 10 x64 Level ELO's (WIP)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 15, 2019</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73164\">New chess engine: Rustic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 23, 2020</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75129\">Progress on Rustic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel Vanthoor</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 16, 2020</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228172538\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 69/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 142/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7721-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228172538 and revision id 24898\n -->\n"
